kel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus concentricus]]'' {{Au|(Lour.) Hjelmq.}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus confertus]]'' {{Au|Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus confinis]]'' {{Au|S.H.Huang ex Y.C.Hsu & H.W.Jen}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus confragosus]]'' {{Au|(King ex Hook.f.) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus conocarpus]]'' {{Au|(Oudem.) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus coopertus]]'' {{Au|(Blanco) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus corneri]]'' {{Au|S.Julia & Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus corneus]]'' {{Au|(Lour.) Rehder}} \n** [[Lithocarpus corneus var. hainanensis|var. ''hainanensis'']] {{Au|(Merr.) C.C.Huang & Y.T.Chang}} \n** [[Lithocarpus corneus var. zonatus|var. ''zonatus'']] {{Au|C.C.Huang & Y.T.Chang}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus cottonii]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus craibianus]]'' {{Au|Barnett}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus crassifolius]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus crassinervius]]'' {{Au|(Blume) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus cryptocarpus]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus cucullatus]]'' {{Au|C.C.Huang & Y.T.Chang}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus curtisii]]'' {{Au|(King ex Hook.f.) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus cyclophorus]]'' {{Au|(Endl.) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus cyrtocarpus]]'' {{Au|(Drake) A.Camus}} \n\n==D==\n* ''[[Lithocarpus dalatensis]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus damiaoshanicus]]'' {{Au|C.C.Huang & Y.T.Chang}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus daphnoideus]]'' {{Au|(Blume) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus dasystachyus]]'' {{Au|(Miq.) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus dealbatus]]'' {{Au|(Hook.f. & Thomson ex Miq.) Rehder}} \n** [[Lithocarpus dealbatus subsp. leucostachyus|subsp. ''leucostachyus'']] {{Au|(A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus debaryanus]]'' {{Au|(Warb.) Markgr.}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus dinhensis]]'' {{Au|(Hickel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus dodonaeifolius]]'' {{Au|(Hayata) Hayata}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus dolichostachys]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus ducampii]]'' {{Au|(Hickel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n\n==E==\n[[File:Lithocarpus edulis7.jpg|thumb|''Lithocarpus edu