ei]]'' {{Au|(Hickel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus platycarpus]]'' {{Au|(Blume) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus platyphyllus]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus polystachyus]]'' {{Au|(Wall. ex A.DC.) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus porcatus]]'' {{Au|Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus proboscideus]]'' {{Au|(Hickel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus propinquus]]'' {{Au|C.C.Huang & Y.T.Chang}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus psammophilus]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus pseudokunstleri]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus pseudomagneinii]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus pseudomoluccus]]'' {{Au|(Blume) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus pseudoreinwardtii]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus pseudosundaicus]]'' {{Au|(Hickel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus pseudovestitus]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus pseudoxizangensis]]'' {{Au|Z.K.Zhou & H.Sun}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus pulcher]]'' {{Au|(King) Markgr.}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus pulongtauensis]]'' {{Au|Cannon & Xi}}\n* ''[[Lithocarpus pusillus]]'' {{Au|Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus pycnostachys]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n\n==Q==\n* ''[[Lithocarpus qinzhouicus]]'' {{Au|C.C.Huang & Y.T.Chang}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus quangnamensis]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus quercifolius]]'' {{Au|C.C.Huang & Y.T.Chang}} \n\n==R==\n* ''[[Lithocarpus rassa]]'' {{Au|(Miq.) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus recurvatus]]'' {{Au|Barnett}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus reinwardtii]]'' {{Au|(Korth.) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus revolutus]]'' {{Au|Hatus. ex Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus rhabdostachyus]]'' {{Au|(Hickel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus rigidus]]'' {{Au|Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus robinsonii]]'' {{Au|Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus rosthornii]]'' {{Au|(Schottky) Barnett}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus rotundatus]]'' {{Au|(Blume) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus rouletii]]'' {{Au|(Hickel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus rufescens]]'' {{Au|Barnett}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus rufovillosus]]'' {{Au|(Markgr.) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus ru