us) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus brachystachyus]]'' {{Au|Chun}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus braianensis]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus brassii]]'' {{Au|Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus brevicaudatus]]'' {{Au|(Skan) Hayata}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus brochidodromus]]'' {{Au|S.Julia & Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus bullatus]]'' {{Au|Hatus. ex Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus burkillii]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n\n==C==\n* ''[[Lithocarpus calolepis]]'' {{Au|Y.C.Hsu & H.Wei Jen}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus calophyllus]]'' {{Au|Chun ex C.C.Huang & Y.T.Chang}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus cambodiensis]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus campylolepis]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus cantleyanus]]'' {{Au|(King ex Hook.f.) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus carolinae]]'' {{Au|(Skan ex Dunn) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus castellarnauianus]]'' {{Au|(Vidal) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus caudatifolius]]'' {{Au|(Merr.) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus caudatilimbus]]'' {{Au|(Merr.) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus celebicus]]'' {{Au|(Miq.) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus cerifer]]'' {{Au|(Hickel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus chevalieri]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus chienchuanensis]]'' {{Au|Hu}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus chifui]]'' {{Au|Chun & Tsiang}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus chittagongus]]'' {{Au|(King ex Hook.f.) Merr.}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus chiungchungensis]]'' {{Au|Chun & P.C.Tam}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus chrysocomus]]'' {{Au|Chun & Tsiang}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus cinereus]]'' {{Au|W.Y.Chun & C.C.Huang}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus clathratus]]'' {{Au|(Seemen) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus cleistocarpus]]'' {{Au|(Seemen) Rehder & E.H.Wilson}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus clementianus]]'' {{Au|(King ex Hook.f.) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus coalitus]]'' {{Au|(Hickel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus coinhensis]]'' {{Au|(Hickel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus concentricus]]'' {{Au|(Lour.) Hjelmq.}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus confertus]]'' {{Au|Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus confinis]]'' {{Au|S.H.Huang ex Y.C.Hsu & H.W.Jen}}