amus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus gracilis]]'' {{Au|(Korth.) Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus guinieri]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus gymnocarpus]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n\n==H==\n[[File:Lithocarpus harlandii Jian-Shih.jpg|thumb|''Lithocarpus harlandii'']]\n* ''[[Lithocarpus haipinii]]'' {{Au|Chun}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus hallieri]]'' {{Au|(Seemen) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus hancei]]'' {{Au|(Benth.) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus handelianus]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus harlandii]]'' {{Au|(Hance ex Walp.) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus harmandii]]'' {{Au|(Hickel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus hatusimae]]'' {{Au|Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus havilandii]]'' {{Au|(Stapf) Barnett}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus hendersonianus]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus henryi]]'' {{Au|(Seemen) Rehder & E.H.Wilson}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus himalaicus]]'' {{Au|C.C.Huang & Y.T.Chang}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus honbaensis]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus howii]]'' {{Au|Chun}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus hypoglaucus]]'' {{Au|(Hu) C.C.Huang ex Y.C.Hsu & H.W.Jen}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus hystrix]]'' {{Au|(Korth.) Rehder}} \n\n==I==\n* ''[[Lithocarpus imperialis]]'' {{Au|(Seemen) Markgr.}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus indutus]]'' {{Au|(Blume) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus irwinii]]'' {{Au|(Hance) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus iteaphyllus]]'' {{Au|(Hance) Rehder}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus ithyphyllus]]'' {{Au|Chun ex H.T.Chang}} \n\n==J==\n* ''[[Lithocarpus jacksonianus]]'' {{Au|A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus jacobsii]]'' {{Au|Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus javensis]]'' {{Au|Blume}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus jenkinsii]]'' {{Au|(Benth.) C.C.Huang & Y.T.Chang}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus jordanae]]'' {{Au|(Villanueva) Rehder}} \n\n==K==\n* ''[[Lithocarpus kalkmanii]]'' {{Au|S.Julia & Soepadmo}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus kamengii]]'' {{Au|K.C.Sahni & H.B.Naithani}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus kawakamii]]'' {{Au|(Hayata) Hayata}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus kemmaratensis]]'' {{Au|(Hickel & A.Camus) A.Camus}} \n* ''[[Lithocarpus keningauensis]]'' {{Au|S